    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Office of the Jewish Messenger</placeName>,</p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>119 West Houston Street</placeName>,</p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>Aug 12. 1863</date>.</p>
            <p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>, V. P. oc.</p>
            <p>Rev &amp; Dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I have first<lb/> learned from my uncle <persName>Rev D. W.
                    Isaacs</persName><lb/> of <placeName>Manchester</placeName>, that the body of
                the<lb/> lamented <persName>Henry I. Hart</persName> has been exhumed<lb/> &amp;
                will be brought on to <placeName>New York</placeName> for<lb/> internment. Under
                this state of the<lb/> case, I presume you would desire to<lb/> have a meeting of
                the Executive<lb/> Committee convened, so that proper steps<lb/> may be taken, to
                attend the obsequies, &amp;c.<lb/> The body is expected by the “<placeName>City
                    of<lb/> Washington</placeName>” which left <placeName>Liverpool</placeName> last<lb/>
                <date>Wednesday</date> &amp; is due next <date>Monday</date> or<lb/>
                <date>Tuesday</date>. I shall, accordingly, call<lb/> a meeting for
                    <date>Monday</date> Evening at<lb/> 8 o'clock. If it will be in your<lb/> power
                to attend, so much the better.</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p rend="indent(1)">On consultation with one or two of<lb/> the committee, I have
                concluded to<lb/> convene the meeting at <placeName>119 West<lb/> Houston
                    St.</placeName></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Hoping to have the pleasure of<lb/> seeing you, or, if your presence
                is<lb/> impracticable, of receiving any<lb/> suggestions you may have to<lb/> offer,
                I am, Rev &amp; dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">Respectfully Yours,</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <persName role="author">M. J. Isaacs</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
